name: The Clench - Cemetery Logo
description:
Word on the ranch is that it's about damn time we made some apparel available to you good folks out there, so here we go.

Made of the finest freshly-picked cotton, lovingly handcrafted by the finest needle workers and costumiers this side of the Mississippi, and emblazoned with our trademark aesthetic, these tees just might be the very thing your wardrobe needs. At the very least, your heavy rep is likely to get even heavier.

Available in S, M, L and XL only. Please specify which one you want.

name: T-shirt and album bundle
description:
Holy patootie! What's this, some sort of bargain?
Damn straight it is. Buy our new t-shirt bundled with our not-that-new CD for the bargainlicious price you see before you.
